name: Mijia Induction Cooker Youth Edition White
description:
• MIJIA Induction Cooker Youth Edition 
  • High-power coil, nine gears, variable frequency control temperature.
  • 2100 power, thickened dense coils, low power continuous heating.
 
Beautiful body, round shape is easy to store.
 
Rotate the button, one button to open.
 
Quick press to start
 
Rotate the button to adjust the firepower
 
Quick press pause / long press is off.
 
156mm coil, high firepower.
The thickened energy-enhancing coil, double-layer superimposed design, uniform magnetic coverage, more uniform heating, and greatly improved performance.
 
2100W
High firepower and rapid heating.
 
Stable Heating
The traditional induction cooker will appear intermittent heating problems, the unstable temperature will lead to cooking failure. in order to solve this problem, xiaomi induction cooker using dual-frequency heating technology, which can give you such as traditional stove cooking experience.Tookfun
 
Double anti-slip, stable and durable.
The panel is made of high temperature resistant non-slip silicone to make the pot more stable.
It can be disassembled and easy to clean.
 
Hot and cold air duct isolation structure, adding fans.
Internal cooling, Increase the life of the product.
 
Built-in system high temperature protection, safe and secure.
Built-in temperature sensor, when the temperature reaches the preset temperature, it will automatically stop heating.
When there is no pot, the heating is automatically stopped.
 
Beautiful and performance coexist, convenient, and delicious.Tookfun
moreInformation:
Mijia Induction Cooker Youth Edition White Details:

Xiaomi Youth Edition induction cooker using dual-frequency heating technology, which can give you a cooking experience such as the traditional stove
Low-temperature cooking
